  "3155830": {
    "name": "白创纪 - Genesis of Pure White",
    "steam_appid": 3155830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155830/extras/7c8a281234949d8d6b233e3727870750.avif?t=1767724954\" width=610 height=150 /></span><strong>《白创纪》是一款包含解谜探索与弹幕战斗的冒险RPG。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>个性鲜明的角色，独具风格的副本关卡，生动的演出为你带来沉浸式体验！</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155830/extras/15f78fd65d93454bb69f82ffcb25328b.avif?t=1767724954\" width=610 height=150 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某天，神秘的光柱突然降临世间， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不仅赋予了人们异能，同时也带来了迷雾与怪物，逐渐吞噬着地表的一切。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要想彻底解决它，唯有通关并关闭光柱分裂出的七个<strong>「副本」</strong>，才能解开其中的秘密。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“加入我吧...我是最强的，能带你解开光柱的秘密。”</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着红中庭学院新生考试的开幕，眼前所出现自称最强的，却是一个畏畏缩缩的懦弱邋遢小鬼， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由一群问题儿童所组成的新兴小队，目标却是闯过七个副本拯救世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一切…究竟会如何发展呢？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155830/extras/cec2c1613e169c1625ae8959cecb6133.avif?t=1767724954\" width=630 height=288 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155830/extras/a8e39b106e9273f02bc7eb17bd0e66cf.avif?t=1767724954\" width=610 height=150 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>本游戏采用辩论战与弹幕战两种机制，请尽可能收集线索线索完成辩论，并且在弹幕战斗中存活。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155830/extras/c162840c1eb081b91692237b7f2be1b7.avif?t=1767724954\" width=610 height=227 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >弹幕战斗：当你捕捉到眼睛形状的破绽时，可选择使用指挥或探索按钮。  <br>指挥按钮可以触发队友技能，帮助规避弹幕伤害或压缩战斗时间；  <br>探索按钮则会增加敌人的暴走值，并在后续副本中获得辩论线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*注意：在弹幕战中只能使用WASD进行方向移动。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155830/extras/fccdcf35d9e895e180d7dbd2052cc0c9.avif?t=1767724954\" width=610 height=227 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >辩论战斗：玩家需要判断敌人观点的正确与否，逐步削弱其怀疑值。 <br>如果对方的观点错误，玩家可以使用现有线索进行反驳，从而赢得对方的信任。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>此外，游戏还包含少量追逐战和解谜元素，进一步丰富了玩法和体验。</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155830/extras/665031fd4e43c58b41ff3f3db05f8af1.avif?t=1767724954\" width=610 height=150 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用wasd者方向键移动。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用shift进行奔跑。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用空格对话调查。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用x键打开菜单，鼠标进行选择。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155830/extras/ab1c54bd78d638466ce819c3bdce0db4.avif?t=1767724954\" width=610 height=150 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >美术/剧本/制作：幽琴</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音乐：kan9，淘声网，小森平</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UI:千冥暗雪</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >插件：黑白</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发行：梦结界工作室</p></li></ul>",
